      <title>拜登退出选举带来不确定性，黄金价格保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/gold-climbs-as-us-election-chaos-escalates-after-biden-drops-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场权衡总统乔·拜登结束连任竞选的决定，黄金价格保持稳定，这引发了人们对其对唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫的机会产生影响的新疑问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/gold-climbs-as-us-election-chaos-escalates-after-biden-drops-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 23:03:32 GMT</pubDate>
